text:

50 on Fire is coming up fast, with the first meetup next week and the main event on Dec. 10. Nominations are rolling in, with trailblazers and trendsetters from all over the area making an appearence. While nominations are still open, we wanted to spotlight some of the names that may end up getting called out as a winner in a couple months. 
Be sure to get your nominations in soon, and check out the categories here . Who's already smoldering >> All the tech news in D.C. you need to know.
